<p><span class="caps">ENGLISH</span>:  Inter-imm: italian as a second language at the work place and in the prison context<br />
Schedule 2</p>
<span class="caps">TYPE</span> OF <span class="caps">TRAINING</span> <span class="caps">ACTIVITY</span>
<p><span class="caps">TRAINING</span> <span class="caps">AIMED</span> AT <span class="caps">PARTICIPANTS</span> <span class="caps">RECEIVING</span> :</p>
